SETUP:
Both directories "text" and "styles" should at the same directory level.

To compile adaptations:

1: Edit courseInfo.txt
Contains specific course and institution information to be displayed on title page

2: Edit courseSetup.tex
Contains specific course content for the book:
	 remove content by commenting with '%' at the beginning of line
	 reorder material

To run, type 'make'

To clean directory and remove unnecessary files after compiling, type 'make clean'

There are other options that can been used through the Makefile for special versions of the text.